description: Try our easy to follow Farmhouse Veg Soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Vegetable soup,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Tree nut free,Spring,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,Halal,High fibre,Vegetarian,Vegan,Tomato,Low fat,Peanut free
name: Farmhouse Veg Soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 pkt Maggi apricot chicken recipe base

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in medium saucepan, add onion and carrot, cook for 5 minutes or until softened.
Add zucchini, cook for 2 minutes, and tomatoes, cook for a further 2 minutes.

Combine Maggi apricot chicken recipe base and 3 cups (750mL) of water, add to saucepan with risoni. Bring to the boil, reduce heat; simmer 10-15 minutes or until vegetables are tender and pasta is cooked through.
